{"id":299569610,"lang":"python3","time":"1 year, 5 months","timestamp":1580651304,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"68 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/299569610/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"12.8 MB","code":"from collections import defaultdict\n\nclass Solution:\n    def lengthOfLongestSubstring(self, s):\n        N = len(s)\n        freq_map = defaultdict(int)\n        lp, rp = 0, 0\n        ans = 0\n        while rp < N:\n            char = s[rp]\n            if freq_map[char]==0:\n                freq_map[char] += 1\n                ans = max(ans, rp - lp + 1)\n                rp += 1\n            else:\n                freq_map[char] += 1\n                while freq_map[char] != 1:\n                    lp_char = s[lp]\n                    freq_map[lp_char] -= 1\n                    lp += 1\n                rp += 1\n        return ans\n                    \n                    \n                    \n        \n        ","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
